txt.en: Kindred to the Protectors of Wilderland

You have proven yourself invaluable to the Protectors of Wilderland and have done much to aid the Wells of Langflood and its people. For this, the Protectors of Wilderland now count you among their own.
You must earn Kindred standing with the Protectors of Wilderland
The Protectors of Wilderland count you among their own, and your deeds will be remembered for ages to come.
